                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15A5/473: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Atherton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-08-27T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 27, 1935—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>230. Your 407, August 27, noon, is eminently satisfactory to us. We approve your
                    not making the suggestions contained in the last sentence of our instructions
                    and authorize you to bring them up in your discretion if and when the occasion
                    calls for this.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
